=====Usage notes=====
* {{term|thou|Thou}} is used with the archaic second-person singular of verbs, which usually ends in {{term|-est}}, as in, for example, “Lovest '''thou''' me?” Exceptions (forms without ''s'') include: {{term|art#Verb|art}} (of {{term|be}}), {{term|hast}} (of {{term|have}}), {{term|shalt}} (of {{term|shall}}) and {{term|wilt}} (of {{term|will#Verb|will}}).

